;An Important Change in Firefox: Dedicated Profiles
Važna promjena u Firefoxu: Namjenski profili


;What’s Changed
Šta je promijenjeno


;Before, all Firefox installations were sharing a single profile by default. Now, Firefox provides dedicated profiles for each Firefox installation (this includes installations of Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta, or Firefox ESR). This will make Firefox more stable when switching between Firefox installations on the same computer.
Prije, sve instalacije Firefox-a su podrazumijevano dijelile jedan profil. Sada, Firefox nudi namjenske profile za svaku Firefox instalaciju (to uključuje instalacije Firefox Nightly, Firefox Beta ili Firefox ESR). Ovo će učiniti Firefox stabilnijim prilikom prebacivanja između Firefox instalacija na istom računaru.


;How Dedicated Profiles Work
Kako namjenski profili rade


;Firefox saves information such as bookmarks, passwords and user preferences in a set of files called your profile. This profile is stored in a separate location from the Firefox program files.
Firefox sprema informacije kao što su zabilješke, lozinke i korisničke postavke u skup datoteka koje se nazivaju vaš profil. Ovaj profil je pohranjen na zasebnoj lokaciji u Firefox programskim datotekama.


;The installation you choose as your primary Firefox installation will keep your previously shared profile data like bookmarks, history and passwords.
Instalacija koju izaberete kao primarnu instalaciju Firefoxa će zadržati prethodno podijeljene podatke o profilu kao što su zabilješke, historija i lozinke.


;You have not lost any personal data or customizations. Any previous profile data is safe and attached to the first Firefox installation that was opened after this change.
Niste izgubili nikakve lične podatke ili prilagodbe. Svi prethodni podaci o profilu su sigurni i priključeni na prvu Firefox instalaciju koja je otvorena nakon ove promjene.


;All of your Firefox installations will now have separate profiles.
Sve vaše instalacije za Firefox sada će imati odvojene profile.


;What You Need to Do
Šta trebate učiniti


;If you do nothing, each installation will have a separate profile. This means your profile data will be different on each installation of Firefox.
Ako ne učinite ništa, svaka instalacija će imati poseban profil. To znači da će se podaci vašeg profila razlikovati na svakoj instalaciji Firefoxa.


;You can change which installation uses which profile using the profile manager. Directions on how to use the profile manager are available on <a href="%(support)s">this support page</a>.
Možete da promijenite koja instalacija koristi koji profil pomoću menadžera profila. Upute o tome kako koristiti menadžera profila možete pronaći na <a href="%(support)s">ovoj stranici za podršku</a>.


;While profiles are now connected to each installation of Firefox, you can use your Firefox Account to keep them in sync. If you would like all of your profile data to be the same on all installations of Firefox, we recommend you sync all of your profiles with a Firefox Account.
Dok su profili sada povezani sa svakom instalacijom Firefox-a, možete da koristite Firefox račun da biste ih sinhronizovali. Ako želite da svi vaši podaci o profilu budu isti na svim instalacijama Firefoxa, preporučujemo da sinhronizujete sve svoje profile sa Firefox računom.


;A Firefox Account is the easiest way to make your profiles consistent on all of your versions of Firefox. You also get additional benefits like sending tabs and secure password storage.
Firefox račun je najlakši način da vaše profile uskladite sa svim vašim verzijama Firefox-a. Dobijate i dodatne pogodnosti kao što su slanje tabova i sigurna pohrana lozinki.


;You’re signed in and ready to start using Sync.
Prijavljeni ste i spremani za korištenje Sinhronizacije.


;We detected that you have installed and opened an older version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Otkrili smo da ste instalirali i otvorili stariju verziju Firefoxa na računaru. Možda ćete morati da preduzmete akciju.


;We detected more than one version of Firefox on your computer. You may need to take action.
Otkrili smo više od jedne verzije Firefox-a na vašem računaru. Možda ćete morati da preduzmete akciju.


